response.original_title: Stevie Ray Vaughan - Live at Rockpalast 1984
response.overview: Live in Loreley St. Goarshausen, Germany on the famous German TV Show Rockpalast, on August 25, 1984.  Songs performed:  Scuttle Buttin  Testify  Voodoo Chile  The Things That I Used To Do  Honey Bee  Love Struck Baby  Cold Shot  Couldn't Stand The Weather  Tin Pan Alley  Pride And Joy  Texas Flood  Little Wing  Third Stone From The Sun  Also includes as bonus material 1988 MTV Europe Special "Life And Times Of Stevie Ray Vaughan" with interview and video clips.
response.title: Stevie Ray Vaughan - Live at Rockpalast 1984
